entries.femaleVariant: Hey choom, listen... BDs – you done any, ever?
Sure, yeah, maybe a couple. Why you askin'?
Thinking of taking a dip, you know...? Money's better.
True that... but I can't recommend that gig. Here, you just sellin' your body. There, you givin' up thoughts, your soul – feel me? Get strange motherfuckers thrashin' around in your bean.
An' that ain't no good feelin, nuh-uh, not no way.
